    "MissionTokens": {
        "Contractor|BountyFPSDescription": [
            "I want you to focus your efforts on one [TargetName]. You should be able to find them and at The cave can only be accessed on foot.. My sources indicate that they might not be alone. The cave can only be accessed on foot.\n\nAt the very least kill [TargetName]. The others are none of my concern.\n\nEarnestly,\nVaughn",
            "It appears that one [TargetName] has been making quite the impression. I received multiple commissions to see them killed. Lucky for them since the individual offers were not high enough, but pooled together are more than sufficient.\n\nFind them at The cave can only be accessed on foot.. I was made to understand that they will not be alone so caution is the key. The cave can only be accessed on foot.\n\nEarnestly,\nVaughn",
            "The time has come for one [TargetName] to bid adieu to this cruel world. \n\nYou will find them and some faithful companions sequestered at The cave can only be accessed on foot.. The cave can only be accessed on foot.\n\nThey think that teamwork will be enough to overcome your considerable skills. I would wager my credits on you.\n\nEarnestly,\nVaughn"
